<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">10月18日，全国高等院校数智化企业经营沙盘大赛（本科组）全国总决赛在南京圆满落幕。117支参赛队伍经过沙盘模拟对抗、管理创新路演两个赛段的比拼，我院学子任夏雨、史文豪、熊丘、邓晶萍获得大赛一等奖，我院老师万丽霞、张沁雨获得一等奖优秀指导老师。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815558375.png" alt="1761815558375.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815558375.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815595191.png" alt="1761815595191.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815595191.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在赛事进程中，面对激烈竞争与动态市场，队员们始终保持镇定、协同作战。他们凭借过硬的专业素养与深厚的实战积累，及时优化调整策略。团队内部职责清晰、交流高效，既充分释放了每位成员的特长优势，又汇聚成无强大的团队合力。无论是应对突发状况，还是捕捉各种细微变动，他们都展现出极强的临场应变能力与高超的商业洞察力。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">最终，我院参赛团队凭借亮眼的综合表现，取得全国一等奖的佳绩!这不仅是对队员们日夜奋战、不懈努力的最佳回馈，更生动印证了学院在教学实践与高素质人才培育方面的卓越成效。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815625019.png" alt="1761815625019.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815625019.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815652095.png" alt="1761815652095.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815652095.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815911580.png" alt="1761815911580.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815911580.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815930390.png" alt="1761815930390.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815930390.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815954775.png" alt="1761815954775.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761815954775.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761816012220.png" alt="1761816012220.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1761816012220.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">少年的足迹印在每一片创新的沃土上。这些奖项是汗水的勋章，更是梦想的序章。学校将持续鼓励并大力支持此类实践创新活动，为同学们搭建更多展示才华、提升能力的平台，助力大家在实践中成长，在探索中成就梦想！</span></p>